- Per-kernel sanity: DS4_ROCM_SYNC_EACH=1 DS4_ROCM_TIME=1 ./ds4 ... and confirm router_select / hc_expand drop.

Add a new tie-order test case for top-k argmax (two experts with equal score; lowest index must win).

Expected total speedup from items 1+2: 13-17 ms/tok recovered. Decode 71 ms -> 54-58 ms = 14 -> 17.5-18.5 t/s. Headroom remains in matmul_f16 (17 ms/tok, unaudited) and routed_moe_one (12 ms/tok, near 188 GiB/s).

